modShortDescription: Provides vending machines that act as fully stocked traders that players can place in their bases.
modDescription:
Provides vending machines that act as fully stocked traders that players can place in their bases. These can be purchased from a trader or crafted at a workbench.

This mod works on servers with no client side installation necessary, or on single player games.

**[Download](https://imadeyoursite.com/7days/BModEconomyBoost.zip)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/24958-brians-mods-for-alpha-196/).
